{"tid":2452303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"耳傷、糖尿困擾　趙家賢留醫赤柱監獄醫院","createTime":"2021-03-18T18:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T01:49:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7c1dbdc0d44a7be96bdf1fe44a13a44d290d78","tid":2452303,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T18:09:40.000Z","msg":"47名民主派人士被控串謀顛覆國家政權罪，至今僅11人獲准保釋，其餘各人被還柙獄中，未審先囚。葵青區議會主席、民主黨單仲偕昨探望黨友尹兆堅，形容尹面型較以前瘦削，但鬥志仍在，又鼓勵牆外人「要加油、頂住」。黃于喬指男友劉頴匡繼續做「黐信封」工作，惟速度竟較年齡大他一倍的囚友慢。關注囚權的立法會前議員邵家臻和張超雄指趙家賢受健康問題困擾，身在監獄醫院，「人明顯疲態」。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄和邵家臻到赤柱監獄探望趙家賢，張稱趙精神不錯，但因身體一向有毛病，「都辛苦㗎」。邵家臻在社交網站指趙家賢耳朵受創，有高血壓、糖尿、五十肩等，身在監獄醫院，「人明顯疲態」，慨嘆「佢向來小心，竟被國安法搞上，真是不明白，至今仍不太接受」。<br />\n<br />\n邵續指趙家賢暫未有收音機，加上獄中資訊有限，不知道范國威辭任區議員，亦不知岑敖暉、朱凱廸已經落『大棚』生活」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210319/L2BO5HRKGBEYPCKWIZRZXZDWBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210319%2FL2BO5HRKGBEYPCKWIZRZXZDWBU%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBShURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=356eb5ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210319%2FL2BO5HRKGBEYPCKWIZRZXZDWBU%2F&h=c82940a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210319/L2BO5HRKGBEYPCKWIZRZXZDWBU/</a>"},{"pid":"39bd73a8bf9acfa32cbf6062e99551bb7268adf7","tid":2452303,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e71790a341be98884d3d57fc03b07bafa6f2a7","tid":2452303,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583f484966526d5e6ebae2da5a9d4381a8cc6b55","tid":2452303,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}